          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12121659"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the phosphatidylinositol 3'-kinase (PI3K), an important mediator of the CD28 signaling pathway [2], [3]. This node is important for the metabolic shift neccesary upon T cell activation [4].</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="1501" y="223" style=""/>
    </node>
