          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=30692200"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the second messenger phosphatidylinositol 3,4,5-trisphosphate (PIP3), important in the PI3K signaling pathway [2], [3].</comment>
