          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17548359"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the molecule diacylglycerol, an important second messenger downstream teh TCR signaling pathway [2].</comment>
      </annotation>
