          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17544292"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the kinase PKC theta, a Ca independent and DAG dependent PKC [2], [3].</comment>
      </annotation>
