          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=29757466"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the NADPH-oxidase enzyme complex assembled at the cytoplasmic membrane, which is activated upon TCR activation [2] It is composed of several subunits [4]. It is a source of cROS.</comment>
      </annotation>
