        </linklist>
        <comment>HGNC:3062
20682913

This node represents the nonphagocytic NADPH oxidase enzime DUOX1. It is a ROS source important for the early TCR signaling [2].
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="1354" y="594" style="ROS or ROS source"/>
    </node>
