          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=15534200"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represents the phosphatase with sequence homology to tensin (PTEN), a negative modulator of PI3K signaling pathway. It is a redox sensitive node [2]. </comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="1789" y="291" style="redox sensitive"/>
