        </linklist>
        <comment>This node represent the cytosol ATP/ADP ratio. It is an indicator of the Warburg metabolism of proliferative cells supported mainly by the cytosol, different from the oxidative metabolism of quiescent cells supported mainly by the mitochondria [2].
</comment>
      </annotation>
